title: [I-Anime]Shin Prince of Tennis V1. ch.2
description:
Volume 1 Chapter 2 from Shin Tennis no Oujisama (New Prince of Tennis) , it is a sezcon seazon. Made by Romanian scanlating team I-Anime.

Sub language: Romanian.

Description 
The purported advertisement from the Jump Square issue says that everything in The Prince of Tennis up to now has been "prologue" and that "a new legend for [the main character] Ryoma and the others will begin."
